ES OF THE MAGICIAN. The shaman epic right click is also just that, A RIGHT CLICK SPESIFICALLY DESIGNED TO ADD DAMAGE FOR THE SHAMAN.<br /><br />The Holgresh Elder Beads / Stalking probes are what? An item designed for scouting an area that you dont know much about, or to see where spawns are without risking your life, with side effects that just happen to be beneficial for a necromancer.<br /><br />God forbid this game actually keeps some of its integrity and isnt DULLED DOWN enough with every new expansion making everything so INCREDIBLY more easy to do than previously.</span id="msg"></font><br><br></td>
