                      <td valign="top" height="100%"><font face="arial" size="2" color="#000000"><span class="spnMessageText" id="msg"> Well, technically, it's probably the SKs screwing us over on this one, although it's not really their fault. The point being that their mana taps work on the eyes, thus the SK can tap an eye in between fights to juice up mana for his group. Necro mana taps won't work on eyes, but due to how the SK one is some sort of special one (look it up if you need the details) it will still work for mana tapping on an eye. IMO this would be the strongest reason why SoE would consider making eyes untappable... they don't really care about HP tapping anything, they never have, it's mana tapping that they have always freaked about. Pure and Simple.</span id="msg"></font><br><br></td>
